<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Novellus said lowered.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Novellus said lowered.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Prudential Securities downgraded Novellus Systems Inc to hold from buy, a source at the firm said.</p>
<p>-- The stock fell sharply on Monday after the company said it had lost a patent infringement trial and said its first-quarter earnings fell sharply from the same period a year ago.</p>
<p>-- It was off one at 52 in early trading.</p>
</text>
